{"tid":986159,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【流感肆虐　血庫需求增　紅十字會籲市民捐血】","createTime":"2019-01-18T08:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:35:18.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bda8b46aaa017b2f3fb8f78f3ae07cca21fd4c37","tid":986159,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>流感肆虐　血庫需求增　紅十字會籲市民捐血</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fbkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001.html&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7TACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=b4d9f24e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/photo/bkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190118162947\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190118162947&h=5eaac5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捐血救人！<br />\n<br />\n香港正值流感高峰期，加上天氣寒冷，紅十字會輸血服務中心表示血液需求大增，惟捐血人數不足，以致血液收集量持續偏低。中心呼籲市民捐血，以支撐病人渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n因應農曆新年假期將至，中心希望市民能在離港旅行前先捐血。現凡於捐血站或捐血流動熱點成功捐血，即可獲得「I&rsquo;m a Blood Donor」系列禮品一份及「捐得有型」利是封一套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/photo/bkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190118162947\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190118155754710-0118_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190118162947&h=ea503953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功捐血可獲得利是封一套。數量有限，送完即止。"}]}